      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745827753,
      "updated": 1745827776
    },
    {
      "id": "680f37a000000000007ec408",
      "text": "↑2025/4/28",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745827745,
      "updated": 1745827753
    },
    {
      "id": "680f37da00000000007ec40b",
      "text": " そろそろ限界だろうか、背景がちょっとシンプルになったぐらいで変化しなくなってきた[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745827802,
      "updated": 1745827836
    },
    {
      "id": "680f381d00000000007ec40c",
      "text": " さらにポリゴン数を減らしてと依頼したら、「すみませんもう減らせません」とギブアップしてきた。勝った[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745827869,
      "updated": 1745827895
    },
    {
      "id": "680db4380000000000209924",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/50dd0263708b8968eee041c408812075]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745728567,
      "updated": 1745728616
    },
    {
      "id": "680db4380000000000209925",
      "text": "↑2025/04/27",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745728567,
      "updated": 1745728573
    },
    {
      "id": "680db4740000000000209927",
      "text": " 目から光が消えたw[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745728627,
      "updated": 1745733117
    },
    {
      "id": "680dc7010000000000f39d3e",
      "text": " 大分良い感じになってきたぞ[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745733378,
      "updated": 1745733394
    },
    {
      "id": "680dc74b0000000000f39d3f",
      "text": " \t世界ってこの解像度で表現できるんだ……",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745733452,
      "updated": 1745733468
    },
    {
      "id": "680dc75d0000000000f39d40",
      "text": " \tもう2段階くらいいけそうだぞ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745733469,
      "updated": 1745733482
    },
    {
      "id": "6806ff940000000000a7917a",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/8d6cade1505e70f9e8b0d9edd326b269]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745289108,
      "updated": 1745289111
    },
    {
      "id": "6806ff8e0000000000a79179",
      "text": "↑ 2025/4/22　ポリゴン減らしつつ明るめにしてもらった",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745289102,
      "updated": 1745289127
    },
    {
      "id": "6806ffad0000000000a7917d",
      "text": "　右目に光が戻った",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745289133,
      "updated": 1745289142
    },
    {
      "id": "6808c81900000000000ab8ca",
      "text": "　背景の抽象化が著しい[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745405977,
      "updated": 1745405990
    },
    {
      "id": "68059dab0000000000cecca0",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/7d87aca353f29fdc09b10d7446a1147e]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745198507,
      "updated": 1745198523
    },
    {
      "id": "68059da30000000000cecc9f",
      "text": "↑ 2025/4/21 だいぶ角ばってきたぞ ",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745198500,
      "updated": 1745198551
    },
    {
      "id": "6805a2b1000000000076c52c",
      "text": "\t右目に変化😆[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1745199794,
      "updated": 1745199803
    },
    {
      "id": "6805a8a50000000000b9b594",
      "text": "\t徐々に明度が落ちている？[つばくろ.icon]",
      "userId": "664f31d71da538001d776cca",
      "created": 1745201316,
      "updated": 1745201358
    },
    {
      "id": "6805a966000000000047a8cc",
      "text": "\t 全体的に暗めになっちゃってきてますね。[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745201509,
      "updated": 1745201533
    },
    {
      "id": "6805a8e60000000000d818cd",
      "text": "\tちょっと縮んでる😁[cak.icon]",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1745201382,
      "updated": 1745201407
    },
    {
      "id": "6805a9aa000000000047a8cd",
      "text": "\t ホントだ。縮んでる[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1745201576,
      "updated": 1745201596
    },
    {
